channel.title: Changing teleEffects
channel.description: Hey Mopar. Im making a city teleport. When you click the teleport it brings up the Frame164 and it has 3 choices. How do i make the choices teleport me somewhere?!

item.title: Changing teleEffects
item.dc:creator: @xI_c_E xI c E
item.description:
@xI_c_E wrote:

Each option has a different case.

1st - 9167
2nd - 9168
3rd - 9169

Simply add which teleEffect under which option you want.

Example for 1st option:

case 9167: if(teleEffect == whatever number) { teleport to x .. teleport to y .. } break;
